  <p><strong>Benefits of PDF preview</strong></p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><strong>Page break</strong>: In the PDF preview, you can view exactly how the page breaks in the letter affect its output. </li> 
   <li><strong>Final preview</strong>: In the PDF preview, you can view the exact formatting and appearance of the letter as the letter will appear in its output.</li> 
  </ul> 
  <p>For information on scripting support in PDF forms, see <a href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/livecycle/11.0/ScriptingSupport/index.html" target="_blank">Scripting Support</a>. </p> 
